Steps to install SASS:
1. Verified Node.js and npm are installed using the commands:
   - node -v
   - npm -v
2. Navigated to the project directory:
   - cd Desktop\FE ALX AFRICA\PRODEV FRONTEND\alx-intermediate-frontend
3. Installed SASS using the following command:
   - npm install sass
4. Verified the installation using:
   - npx sass --version
